 Post.Bid.Ship. gives me a fast and easy way to host private auctions for my spot market freight.  My regular carriers find Post.Bid.Ship. easy to use and an efficient way to manage freight auctions they are invited to.- John Cristelli Transportation and Logistics Specialist TruckItNow TransportationAchieving Oracle Validated Integration gives our customers confidence that the integration between Post.Bid.Ship. and Oracle Transportation Management is functionally sound and performs as tested.- Derek Gittoes Vice President, Supply Chain Management Product Strategy Oracle


