About Us




Post.Bid.Ship. is an exciting technology company based in sunny Scottsdale, Arizona. From our origins as a business school project at the University of Arizona, Post.Bid.Ship. grew to become a venture backed company serving the enterprise shipper market. Our award-winning and Oracle Validated Integration was built by a team of dedicated entrepreneurs and technologists passionate about the transportation industry.

PostBidShip originated at The University of Arizona, where classmates Jarret Hamstreet, Cody Nicholls and Micky Thompson created the original venture concept during their graduate studies at the McGuire Center for Entrepreneurship.  After winning the University’s 2010 “Best Venture Grand Prize,” Hamstreet, Nicholls and Thompson launched PostBidShip following their graduation.  A two-time winner of the State of Arizona’s “Arizona Innovation Challenge,” PostBidShip became an online commercial freight marketplace serving over 11,000 users before evolving into an enterprise technology provider to Fortune 1000 companies.  In 2016, PostBidShip’s innovative spot market freight auction technology earned the highly coveted “Oracle Validated Integration” designation with its integration with Oracle Transportation Management (OTM).










