						Company Summary

Post.Bid.Ship is an online transportation marketplace that allows carriers to bid on loads posted by shippers of commercial goods. This streamlines the process of soliciting rate quotes for shippers and reduces their freight costs as a result of competitive bidding, and gives carriers a cost-effective means of reaching shippers nationwide.




