Post.Bid.Ship., Inc. | Scottsdale, AZ, US Startup 






















Start up confidently with Gust Launch: all the legal, accounting, and financial tools you need to start and run your company.






















Overview




Executive Summary




Financials


























Post.Bid.Ship., Inc.

Post.Bid.Ship.'s goal is to become the Priceline.com of the commercial shipping and transportation market.






Stage

$1M in TTM Revenue



Industry

Internet / Web Services



Location

Scottsdale, AZ, US



Currency

USD



Founded

July 2010



Employees

7



Website

postbidship.com

















Company Summary





Post.Bid.Ship. is a web-based software platform that enables transportation providers (known in the industry as "carriers") to bid on hauling loads of freight posted to our website by shippers of commerical goods.  Just like Priceline.com helps hotels sell excess rooms, Post.Bid.Ship. will help carriers sell excess trailer capacity.










