                    SolutionsOracle Validated IntegrationsBConnPost.Bid.Ship offers the commercial freight industry a next-generation online marketplace that communicates and sells truck space in real time. By partnering innovative technologies with convenient bidding and shipping solutions in one automated platform, Post.Bid.Ship. helps brokers, shippers and carriers save money and time.  Post.Bid.Ship currently counts as members six of the largest 10 trucking companies in the United States.  The companies “BConn” gives Oracle Transportation Management users the first ever access to the spot market.This integration has achieved: Oracle Validated Integration with  Supply Chain Management (SCM)










